To show content on different screen sizes:

Small screens: block sm:hidden md:hidden lg:hidden xl:hidden
Medium screens: hidden sm:block md:hidden lg:hidden xl:hidden
Large screens: hidden sm:hidden md:block lg:hidden xl:hidden
Extra-large screens: hidden sm:hidden md:hidden lg:block xl:hidden


To hide content on different screen sizes:

Small screens: hidden sm:block md:block lg:block xl:block
Medium screens: block sm:hidden md:block lg:block xl:block
Large screens: block sm:block md:hidden lg:block xl:block
Extra-large screens: block sm:block md:block lg:block xl:hidden